high_descs: Turn and face the dishes in the kitchen sink.
Pick up the black plate that's in the sink.
Carry the black plate over to the fridge.
Place the plate in the fridge on the top shelf and then remove after it has cooled.
Carry the plate back to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Open the cupboard beneath the right end of the kitchen sink and place the plate inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled plate in the cupboard beneath the sink.

high_descs: Pick up the black plate that's in the sink please.
Turn around and walk to the fridge that's on your left and face it.
Open the fridge and put the plate to the left of the lettuce and then close the door and let it cool off before retrieving it and closing the door.
Turn left and walk to the cupboard.
Open the second cupboard from the right and put the plate down there.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the black plate in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left side of the room.
Chill the black plate in the refrigerator and then pick the plate up and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the cabinets below the sink.
Place the plate in the right cabinet below the sink and then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled black plate in the right cabinet below the sink.
